{"tid":956701,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[瑞和街]觀塘夫婦與中年漢 因駕駛問題群毆被捕","createTime":"2018-12-26T12:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T14:15:14.000Z","uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4cc1b0bf788c4a16a23af04e0c4244d684401689","tid":956701,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】觀塘下午2時有一對夫婦與一名中年漢，因駕駛問題口角繼而動武，一同被捕。<br />\n<br />\n46歲姓徐男子與46歲姓周妻子，以及55歲姓盧男子在觀塘瑞和街因駕駛態度問題爭執，其間夫婦與男子互相用手襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，經初步調查，3人涉嫌在公眾地方打架被捕，案件交由觀塘警區刑事調查隊第五隊跟進。3人清醒被送往聯合醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收到風單野係世界情色王(46歲姓徐男子)、佩雷斯主席(46歲姓周妻子)同拉車福特(55歲姓盧男子)搞出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391996b1f98cc696f5dcb765b2f535ad3c970da0","tid":956701,"uid":70040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:02:20.000Z","msg":"你又知<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你放完觀塘經過見到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447f71a95eb133ea8d2ccb9bdef822ac42b73247","tid":956701,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"391996b1f98cc696f5dcb765b2f535ad3c970da0","tid":956701,"uid":70040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:02:20.000Z","msg":"你又知<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你放完觀塘經過見到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"睇新聞。"},{"pid":"1853239af223d2ff30c1c11e93544ee1bcdaceac","tid":956701,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"你今日又去左觀塘？"},{"pid":"b3ac2f42211fc1ba22b8e6c8aa3b862f5b730313","tid":956701,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1853239af223d2ff30c1c11e93544ee1bcdaceac","tid":956701,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"你今日又去左觀塘？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:08:40.000Z","